        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2980036537" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10682577225309692355">A most staggering depiction of World War I centering on two Canadian Indians who were utilized most effectively as snipers. The story moves back and forth between battles and the men&apos;s early life in the Canadian wilderness. A raw and brutal telling which is at once beautiful and memorable.</span>
  <span id="freeText10682577225309692355" style="display:none">A most staggering depiction of World War I centering on two Canadian Indians who were utilized most effectively as snipers. The story moves back and forth between battles and the men's early life in the Canadian wilderness. A raw and brutal telling which is at once beautiful and memorable.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10682577225309692355" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

